OL,3,COffer from council over Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cdispute 'watered down', says Unite
OL,6,FAn offer put forward by Birmingham
OL,7,FCity Council in a bid to end the bin
OL,8,Fdispute has been "watered down",
OL,9,Faccording to Unite the Union.
OL,11,FThe union - which represents striking
OL,12,Fbin workers - said the offer came
OL,13,Flater than promised and was "not in
OL,14,Fline with the ballpark offer discussed
OL,15,Fat conciliation".
OL,17,FThis is the first time an offer has
OL,18,Fbeen put in writing since the strike
OL,19,Fbegan on 11 March.
