OL,3,COffer from council over Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cdispute 'watered down', says Unite
OL,6,FIn a statement on Saturday (31 May),
OL,7,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,8,Fsaid: "It is important to remind
OL,9,Fpeople what the dispute is about: Bin
OL,10,Fworkers in Birmingham waking up one
OL,11,Fmorning and being told their pay would
OL,12,Fbe cut by up to #8,000. For some up to
OL,13,Fa quarter of their pay. Putting their
OL,14,Fmortgages, rents and livelihoods at
OL,15,Frisk.
