OL,3,COffer from council over Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cdispute 'watered down', says Unite
OL,6,F"The government and the leader of the
OL,7,Fcouncil have been attacking these
OL,8,Fworkers for weeks for defending
OL,9,Fthemselves and their families by
OL,10,Fstriking, whilst briefing the public
OL,11,Fthat these workers should accept an
OL,12,Foffer on the table that never existed.
OL,14,F"After weeks and weeks of saying one
OL,15,Fthing in public and another to
OL,16,Fworkers, the government commissioners
OL,17,Ffinally allow a proposal to be put on
OL,18,Fthe table."
OL,20,F"Deadlines were missed"
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
