OL,3,COffer from council over Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cdispute 'watered down', says Unite
OL,6,FThe union said it will consult with
OL,7,Fits reps over the weekend and will
OL,8,Fgive a further response to the
OL,9,Fproposal ahead of another meeting with
OL,10,FACAS.
OL,12,F"The proposal is not in line with the
OL,13,Fballpark offer discussed at
OL,14,Fconciliation (ACAS) and has clearly
OL,15,Fbeen watered-down by the government
OL,16,Fcommissioners and the leader of the
OL,17,Fcouncil, who were not in the
OL,18,Fnegotiating room.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
