OL,3,COffer from council over Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cdispute 'watered down', says Unite
OL,6,F"Numerous deadlines were missed. In
OL,7,Ffact, what was to be tabled 48 hours
OL,8,Fafter the ACAS talks, arrived as a
OL,9,Fmuch watered-down proposal, yesterday
OL,10,Fevening, three weeks later.
OL,12,F"The actual decision makers now need
OL,13,Fto be in the room at the further ACAS
OL,14,Ftalks."
OL,16,FUnite said it will release further
OL,17,Fdetails of the offer once it has
OL,18,Fconsulted with its reps.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
