OL,3,COffer from council over Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cdispute 'watered down', says Unite
OL,6,FIn response, Birmingham City Council
OL,7,Fsaid: "The council has made an updated
OL,8,Ffair and reasonable offer to Unite via
OL,9,FACAS ` which we are asking them to
OL,10,Fshare with their members for
OL,11,Fconsideration - with a view to
OL,12,Fbringing the ongoing industrial action
OL,13,Fto an end.
OL,15,F"We are hopeful that talks between
OL,16,Fourselves and Unite will continue next
OL,17,Fweek, as we remain committed to
OL,18,Freaching a negotiated settlement to
OL,19,Fend this dispute."
